item.title: About
item.description: नमस्ते राही ! This is Aditi and you have reached my small place on the World Wide Web. 😄 🕶 I’m a final year Computer Engineering undergraduate at College of Engineering, Pune.🇮🇳I’m passionate about programming and computer systems design and domain specific languages. I like to think of myself as a problem solver who prefers to leverage the potential of technology to build a better, efficient and robust solutions. In my college, I’m a core team member of Asscociation of Students of Computer and IT [ASCI].
